quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  23,93,"Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, Ó ṣeé ṣe kí Ó fi ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún wọn hàn mí"
  23,94,"Olúwa mi, má ṣe fi mí sínú ìjọ alábòsí.”"
  23,95,Dájúdájú Àwa lágbára láti fi ohun tí A ṣe ní ìlérí fún wọn hàn ọ́
  23,96,Fi èyí t’ó dára tí àìdára dànù. Àwa nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí wọ́n fi ń ròyìn (Wa)
  23,97,"Sọ pé: \"Olúwa mi, mò ń sádi Ọ́ níbi ròyíròyí t’àwọn èṣù"
  23,98,"Mò ń sádi Ọ́, Olúwa mi, níbi kí wọ́n wá bá mi"
  23,99,"(Wọ́n ń ṣẹ̀mí lọ) títí di ìgbà tí ikú fi máa dé bá ọ̀kan nínú wọn. Ó sì máa wí pé: “Olúwa mi, Ẹ dá mi padà (sílé ayé)"
  23,100,"nítorí kí n̄g lè ṣe iṣẹ́ rere nínú èyí tí mo gbé jù sílẹ̀. Kò rí bẹ́ẹ̀ rárá, dájúdájú ó jẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ kan tí ó kàn ń wí ni, (àmọ́) gàgá ti wà ní ẹ̀yìn wọn títí di ọjọ́ tí A óò gbé wọn dìde. ayẹta òkígbẹ́"
  23,101,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá fọn fèrè oníwo fún àjíǹde, kò níí sí ìbátan láààrin wọn ní ọjọ́ yẹn, wọn kò sì níí bira wọn léèrè ìbéèrè"
  23,102,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí òṣùwọ̀n (iṣẹ́ rere) rẹ̀ bá tẹ̀wọ̀n, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni olùjèrè"
  23,103,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí òṣùwọ̀n (iṣẹ́ rere) rẹ̀ bá fúyẹ́, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni àwọn t’ó ṣe ẹ̀mí ara wọn lófò. Olùṣegbére sì ni wọ́n nínú iná Jahanamọ"
  23,104,"Iná yóò máa jó wọn lójú. Wọn yó sì wà nínú rẹ̀, tí Iná yóò ti bà wọ́n lójú jẹ́"
  23,105,"Ṣé wọ́n kì í ka àwọn āyah Mi fun yín ni, àmọ́ tí ẹ̀ ń pè é nírọ́"
  23,106,"Wọ́n wí pé: \"Olúwa wa, orí burúkú l’ó kọlù wá; àwa sì jẹ́ ìjọ olùṣìnà"
  23,107,"Olúwa wa, mú wa jáde kúrò nínú Iná. Tí a bá fi lè padà (síbi iṣẹ́ ibi nílé ayé), dájúdájú nígbà náà alábòsí ni àwa"
  23,108,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Ẹ tẹ̀rì sínú rẹ̀. Ẹ má ṣe bá Mi sọ̀rọ̀.”"
  23,109,"Dájúdájú igun kan wà nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi, tí wọ́n ń sọ pé: “Olúwa wa, a gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Nítorí náà, foríjìn wá, kí O sì kẹ́ wa. Ìwọ sì l’óore jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú.”"
  23,110,Ṣùgbọ́n ẹ sọ wọ́n di oníyẹ̀yẹ́ tó bẹ́ẹ̀ gẹ́ tí àwọn yẹ̀yẹ́ (yín) fi mu yín gbàgbé ìrántí Mi. Ẹ̀yin sì ń fi wọ́n rẹ́rìn-ín
  23,111,"Dájúdájú Mo san wọ́n ní ẹ̀san ní òní nítorí sùúrù wọn; dájúdájú àwọn, àwọn ni olùjèrè"
  23,112,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"Ọdún mélòó ni ẹ̀yin (aláìgbàgbọ́) lò lórí ilẹ̀ ayé"
  23,113,"Wọ́n wí pé: “A lo ọjọ́ kan tàbí abala ọjọ́ kan, bi àwọn olùṣírò-ọjọ́ léèrè wò.”"
  23,114,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Ẹ kò gbé ilé ayé bí kò ṣe fún ìgbà díẹ̀, tí ó bá jẹ́ pé ẹ mọ̀.”"
  23,115,"Ṣé ẹ lérò pé A kàn ṣẹ̀dá yín fún ìranù ni, àti pé dájúdájú wọn ò níí da yín padà sọ́dọ̀ Wa?”"
  23,116,"Nítorí náà, Allāhu Ọba Òdodo ga. Kò sí ọlọ́hun tí ìjọ́sìn tọ́ sí àfi Òun, Olúwa Ìtẹ́ alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé"
  23,117,"Ẹni tí ó bá pe ọlọ́hun mìíràn pẹ̀lú Allāhu, kò ní ẹ̀rí lọ́wọ́ lórí rẹ̀. Dájúdájú ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ rẹ̀ sì wà lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ kò níí jèrè"
  23,118,"Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, ṣàforíjìn, kí O sì kẹ́ (mi). Ìwọ sì l’óore jùlọ nínú àwọn aláàánú.”"